Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:31.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}夕阳西下之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:36.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}追逐着渐渐消失的影子
